name: #WAGMI
description:
// We're All Gonna Make It //

It might take time, hard work, and a lot of challenges but we're all gonna make it. When we are able to live in security with freedom and not have to worry primarily about survival. We will then be able to focus on how to thrive. Not just ourselves but everyone and everything around us. Then we'll see that we're cultivating our own happiness and creating space for others to be free. In short #WAGMI
